node.title: The disappearance of Carole Baskin's former husband Don Lewis
node.description: An inside look at the puzzling disappearance of the Florida millionaire
node.content: ["An inside look at the puzzling 1997 cold case disappearance of the Florida millionaire.", "Carole Baskin's former husband, millionaire Don Lewis, was reported missing on August 19, 1997. At the time, he and Carole were married and living in Tampa, Florida."]
